versation ended before Mercer could fully address all logistical challenges, but the strength of the later answers was notable.","question":"Did the student provide solid answers to chatbot questions?"},{"score":4,"feedback":"Mercer consistently attempted to justify answers by referencing details from the case. For example, the student justified the need for training by citing the bottleneck created by Dan Evans\'s sole planning role and the \'intuition, experience, and knowledge\' he possessed. The justification for the website and packages was also well-tied to the case\'s description of Dan\'s extensive time spent with non-professional clients and the need to standardize processes for franchising. These justifications effectively drew on the reading material to support the proposed solutions.","question":"Did the student justify the answer using relevant reading information?"}]','liberal',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'gemini-2.5-flash','gemini-2.5-flash',NULL) ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE created_at=VALUES(created_at),student_id=VALUES(student_id),score=VALUES(score),summary=VALUES(summary),criteria=VALUES(criteria),persona=VALUES(persona),hints=VALUES(hints),helpful=VALUES(helpful),liked=VALUES(liked),improve=VALUES(improve),chat_model=VALUES(chat_model),super_model=VALUES(super_model),transcript=VALUES(transcript);
